{"comments":"FontMetrics - OpenType font metric values.\n\nProvides access to the vertical metrics embedded in font files.\nThese values are essential for precise text layout, baseline alignment,\nand vertical rhythm calculations.\n\n## Metrics Overview\n- **UnitsPerEm**: Design grid size (typically 1000 or 2048)\n- **Ascender**: Height above baseline (uppercase + accents)\n- **Descender**: Depth below baseline (descending letters)\n- **XHeight**: Height of lowercase letters without ascenders\n- **CapHeight**: Height of capital letters\n- **LineGap**: Recommended additional line spacing\n\n## Usage\nFont metrics are extracted from font files (via fontkit, opentype.js, etc.)\nand used for layout calculations. All values are in font design units.\nTo convert to pixels: `pixels = designUnits * fontSize / unitsPerEm`\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Complete font metrics from an OpenType font\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["unitsPerEm",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"UnitsPerEm"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["ascender",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"Ascender"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["descender",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"Descender"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["xHeight",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"XHeight"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["capHeight",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"CapHeight"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["lineGap",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"LineGap"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[146,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontMetrics.purs","start":[139,1]},"title":"FontMetrics"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[81,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontMetrics.purs","start":[81,20]},"title":"UnitsPerEm"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"UnitsPerEm"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontMetrics.purs","start":[83,1]},"title":"eqUnitsPerEm"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"UnitsPerEm"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontMetrics.purs","start":[84,1]},"title":"ordUnitsPerEm"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontMetrics"],"UnitsPerEm"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,41],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontMetrics.purs","start":[86,1]},"title":"showUnitsPerEm"}],"comments":"Units per em - design gri